data.title: Reading Lists For BA A&a
data.meta_description: Reading Lists for BA a&A - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides reading lists for candidates taking BA Archaeology and Anthropology at the University of Oxford in 2016-2017. It is divided into sections for Honour Moderations and Final Honour School, with recommended readings for each of the papers within those sections. It also lists optional papers and provides brief descriptions. The readings include textbooks, journal articles, and websites relevant to different topics within the fields of archaeology and anthropology.
